kuri
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:the dog introduced by the pre-European Polynesian settlers
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: Maori dog
Pronunciation:
Notes: variant spellings including goorie/goory q.v.
